EmailTemplate.name: Webinar Followup - Attended
EmailTemplate.subject: IntApp Webinar Followup - Materials Included
EmailTemplate.textOnly:
Hi {!Contact.FirstName},
Thank you for attending the IntApp webinar on the ABA changes to Rule 1.10 last week. I hope you found the event informative.
Attached is the slide deck from the webinar. We will also be mailing you the ALI-ABA article mentioned during the webinar within the next few weeks. If you have not been receiving our risk bulletins please email Lea Simon at Lea.Simon@intapp.com so we can make sure you receive the article.
If you are interested in obtaining CLE credit, we ask that you fill out this survey: http://www.surveymonkey.com/s.aspx?sm=O0orZU45yY1o0UdUDr9_2bZg_3d_3d to help us process your request for CLE credit as quickly as possible. We welcome everyone's feedback, so even if you're not interested in obtaining CLE credit, we would still appreciate your participation in the survey.
A recording of the webinar is now available on our website and can be found at http://www.intapp.com/products/wbwebinars.html.
